https://codeforces.com/contest/1526/problem/C2


Solution : Maintaining a priority_queue(min) of potions taken till now & a variable health. 
          As soon as health < 0.. start removing the negative elements which had been consumed
          earlier as the main motive is to maximize the number of potions consumed.

